/#
 A type used to report how a position originated.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.PositionOriginEnum {
    # The position originated directly from a trade.
    Trade 
    # The position originated from an allocation of a block trade.
    Allocation 
    # The position originated from a novation or post-trade transfer.
    Novation 
    # The position originated from netting or portfolio compression.
    Netting 
    # The position originated from an exercise of a physically-settled option.
    Exercise 

}

Trade.Doc: The position originated directly from a trade.
Trade.Name: Trade

Allocation.Doc: The position originated from an allocation of a block trade.
Allocation.Name: Allocation

Novation.Doc: The position originated from a novation or post-trade transfer.
Novation.Name: Novation

Netting.Doc: The position originated from netting or portfolio compression.
Netting.Name: Netting

Exercise.Doc: The position originated from an exercise of a physically-settled option.
Exercise.Name: Exercise
